     'РЎРѕРїСЂРѕРІРѕР¶РґР°РµРј РєСЂРёС‚РёС‡РЅС‹Рµ Р·Р°РїСѓСЃРєРё: РїСЂРѕРІРµСЂРєР° РіРѕС‚РѕРІРЅРѕСЃС‚Рё, СЃРЅРёР¶РµРЅРёРµ СЂРёСЃРєРѕРІ, РєРѕРЅС‚СЂРѕР»СЊ РёСЃРїРѕР»РЅРµРЅРёСЏ Рё РїРѕСЃС‚СЂРµР»РёР·РЅР°СЏ СЃС‚Р°Р±РёР»РёР·Р°С†РёСЏ.',
     '<p>РљСЂСѓРїРЅС‹Рµ СЂРµР»РёР·С‹ Рё Р·Р°РїСѓСЃРє РЅРѕРІС‹С… РЅР°РїСЂР°РІР»РµРЅРёР№ С‡Р°СЃС‚Рѕ РїСЂРѕРІР°Р»РёРІР°СЋС‚СЃСЏ РЅРµ РёР·-Р·Р° РѕРґРЅРѕР№ РѕС€РёР±РєРё, Р° РёР·-Р·Р° С†РµРїРѕС‡РєРё РјРµР»РєРёС… РЅРµРґРѕСЂР°Р±РѕС‚РѕРє. РњС‹ РїРѕРґРєР»СЋС‡Р°РµРјСЃСЏ Р·Р°СЂР°РЅРµРµ Рё РїСЂРѕРІРµСЂСЏРµРј РєР»СЋС‡РµРІС‹Рµ Р·РѕРЅС‹: РёРЅС„СЂР°СЃС‚СЂСѓРєС‚СѓСЂР°, РёРЅС‚РµРіСЂР°С†РёРё, Р°РЅР°Р»РёС‚РёРєР°, РІРѕСЂРѕРЅРєР°, СѓРІРµРґРѕРјР»РµРЅРёСЏ, fallback-СЃС†РµРЅР°СЂРёРё Рё РіРѕС‚РѕРІРЅРѕСЃС‚СЊ РєРѕРјР°РЅРґС‹ Рє РёРЅС†РёРґРµРЅС‚Р°Рј.</p><p>Р’ РґРµРЅСЊ Р·Р°РїСѓСЃРєР° Рё РїРѕСЃР»Рµ РЅРµРіРѕ РїРѕРґРґРµСЂР¶РёРІР°РµРј РѕРїРµСЂР°С‚РёРІРЅС‹Р№ РєРѕРЅС‚СѓСЂ: РїСЂРёРѕСЂРёС‚РёР·Р°С†РёСЏ Р·Р°РґР°С‡, РґРёР°РіРЅРѕСЃС‚РёРєР°, РєРѕРјРјСѓРЅРёРєР°С†РёСЏ РјРµР¶РґСѓ Р±РёР·РЅРµСЃРѕРј Рё СЂР°Р·СЂР°Р±РѕС‚РєРѕР№, Р±С‹СЃС‚СЂС‹Рµ СЂРµС€РµРЅРёСЏ РїРѕ СЃС‚Р°Р±РёР»РёР·Р°С†РёРё. Р­С‚Рѕ СЃРЅРёР¶Р°РµС‚ РїРѕС‚РµСЂРё Рё РїРѕР·РІРѕР»СЏРµС‚ Р±С‹СЃС‚СЂРµРµ РІС‹Р№С‚Рё РЅР° С€С‚Р°С‚РЅС‹Р№ СЂРµР¶РёРј СЂР°Р±РѕС‚С‹.</p><p>РС‚РѕРіРѕРј СЃС‚Р°РЅРѕРІРёС‚СЃСЏ Р±РѕР»РµРµ РєРѕРЅС‚СЂРѕР»РёСЂСѓРµРјС‹Р№ Р·Р°РїСѓСЃРє СЃ РїРѕРЅСЏС‚РЅРѕР№ РєР°СЂС‚РёРЅРѕР№ СЂРёСЃРєРѕРІ Рё СѓРїСЂР°РІР»СЏРµРјРѕР№ СЂРµР°РєС†РёРµР№ РЅР° РѕС‚РєР»РѕРЅРµРЅРёСЏ. Р”Р»СЏ Р±РёР·РЅРµСЃР° СЌС‚Рѕ РѕР·РЅР°С‡Р°РµС‚ РјРµРЅСЊС€Рµ СЃС‚СЂРµСЃСЃР°, РјРµРЅСЊС€Рµ С„РёРЅР°РЅСЃРѕРІС‹С… РїРѕС‚РµСЂСЊ Рё Р±РѕР»РµРµ РїСЂРѕРіРЅРѕР·РёСЂСѓРµРјС‹Р№ СЂРµР·СѓР»СЊС‚Р°С‚ СЂРµР»РёР·Р°.</p>',
     150, 1, NOW(), NOW()),

    -- EN: group "Website/platform/blog/landing development"
    ('', 'en', 'web-platforms', 'Corporate website for B2B pipeline growth', 'corporate-website-for-b2b-pipeline-growth',
     'We build a corporate website as a sales system: clear value framing, conversion-oriented structure and measurable lead flow.',
     '<p>This service goes far beyond visual design. We map your market context, define decision-making paths for target segments and structure every page around commercial intent. Messaging, trust blocks, offers and CTA logic are aligned to reduce friction and increase conversion quality.</p><p>On the technical side, we implement a scalable foundation: SEO-ready architecture, event tracking, clean routing and A/B-test readiness. Your team can launch new offers, expand sections and optimize pages without breaking existing performance.</p><p>The result is a website that actively supports sales and marketing operations, not just a brand showcase. You get a maintainable growth asset with clear metrics and room for continuous iteration.</p>',
     10, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'web-platforms', 'SEO blog and content growth platform', 'seo-blog-and-content-growth-platform',
     'We create a structured content platform with topic clusters, internal linking and templates designed for organic growth.',
     '<p>Instead of publishing isolated articles, we design a content system where each page strengthens overall domain authority. Taxonomy, URL logic, metadata patterns and editorial templates are built to support sustained organic expansion across high-value topics.</p><p>We also connect content to business outcomes through strategic CTAs, service cross-links and conversion-oriented page components. This keeps pages useful for users while making them effective in lead generation and demand capture.</p><p>You receive an operational framework your team can scale confidently: clear publishing priorities, measurable performance and a repeatable process for SEO-driven growth.</p>',
     20, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'web-platforms', 'Launch landing page for offer validation', 'launch-landing-page-for-offer-validation',
     'High-conversion landing page for fast market testing, campaign traffic and offer validation with clear performance metrics.',
     '<p>When speed matters, structure matters even more. We design landing pages around a single commercial objective: demo request, call, brief submission or pre-sale. Value proposition clarity, objection handling, social proof and CTA sequence are crafted to move users toward action.</p><p>Tracking events, UTM attribution and optimization readiness are included from day one. This allows rapid iteration after launch based on real data rather than assumptions.</p><p>The outcome is a landing asset that helps you validate positioning quickly, reduce wasted traffic spend and reach stable conversion economics faster.</p>',
     30, 1, NOW(), NOW()),

    -- EN: group "Telegram bot development"
    ('', 'en', 'telegram-bots', 'Telegram bot for lead intake and qualification', 'telegram-bot-for-lead-intake-and-qualification',
     'We build Telegram bots that capture requests, qualify users through guided dialogs and push structured leads into your sales flow.',
     '<p>The bot logic is tailored to your funnel: qualification questions, priority scoring, source tagging and clean handoff to managers. This improves response speed and increases lead quality before a human joins the conversation.</p><p>We also implement conversation logs, anti-noise handling and optional nurturing scenarios for leads that are not ready to buy immediately. The result is a controlled and scalable intake channel.</p><p>For B2B teams, this means fewer random chats, better lead context and faster conversion from first touch to qualified opportunity.</p>',
     40, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'telegram-bots', 'Telegram support automation bot', 'telegram-support-automation-bot',
     'Automate first-line customer support in Telegram with FAQ handling, smart routing and context-aware escalation.',
     '<p>Support teams lose speed when routine requests consume most operator time. We design a bot that resolves repetitive issues instantly, gathers the required context and routes complex cases to the right specialist.</p><p>Escalation paths include ticket categorization, priority logic and history transfer, so customers do not repeat themselves and agents start with full context. This improves both service quality and operational efficiency.</p><p>We also add reporting on response time, auto-resolution rates and issue categories, enabling continuous support optimization based on real data.</p>',
     50, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'telegram-bots', 'Internal Telegram alerting and incident bot', 'internal-telegram-alerting-and-incident-bot',
     'Operational Telegram bot for real-time alerts on leads, payments, incidents, API failures and system health events.',
     '<p>We design an event and priority model to deliver meaningful signals without alert fatigue. Critical events reach responsible roles immediately, while lower-priority notifications are grouped or delayed based on business rules.</p><p>Integrations include delivery logging, retry logic, duplicate protection and escalation chains for unresolved incidents. This turns Telegram into a dependable operations interface, not a noisy message stream.</p><p>Your team gains faster reaction cycles, clearer ownership and better control over production-critical workflows.</p>',
     60, 1, NOW(), NOW()),

    -- EN: group "SaaS platform development"
    ('', 'en', 'saas-platforms', 'MVP SaaS platform for fast go-to-market', 'mvp-saas-platform-for-fast-go-to-market',
     'We launch MVP SaaS products with core architecture, account area, access roles and key user flows for rapid validation.',
     '<p>Early-stage SaaS success depends on releasing the right scope at the right speed. We define a minimal viable feature set that can be sold and validated quickly while preserving architectural integrity for future scaling.</p><p>Delivery includes domain modeling, backend/frontend implementation, baseline analytics, QA and production readiness. Monetization prerequisites can be embedded from the start when your business model requires it.</p><p>You get a real product foundation ready for market feedback, iterative growth and investor-grade operational confidence.</p>',
     70, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'saas-platforms', 'SaaS subscriptions, billing and access control', 'saas-subscriptions-billing-and-access-control',
     'Monetization layer for SaaS products: plans, subscriptions, usage limits, payment states and role-based entitlements.',
     '<p>Reliable monetization requires robust product logic. We implement tariff models, trial flows, upgrade/downgrade paths, access rights and lifecycle automation in a way that is transparent for business teams and maintainable for engineering.</p><p>Payment integrations cover webhook handling, edge cases, retries, refunds and status reconciliation. We also expose critical metrics so you can track revenue quality, retention risks and expansion opportunities.</p><p>The result is a stable commercial core that supports scaling without manual operations overhead.</p>',
     80, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'saas-platforms', 'SaaS scaling and technical modernization', 'saas-scaling-and-technical-modernization',
     'We upgrade existing SaaS systems for higher reliability, better performance and sustainable delivery at scale.',
     '<p>As SaaS products grow, technical limitations often become growth bottlenecks. We identify critical constraints across architecture, data layer, performance, release process and observability, then convert findings into a business-prioritized execution plan.</p><p>Implementation is phased to reduce operational risk: targeted refactoring, infrastructure hardening, monitoring improvements and technical debt reduction aligned with product roadmap milestones.</p><p>Your team spends less time firefighting and more time shipping high-impact features that drive recurring revenue.</p>',
     90, 1, NOW(), NOW()),

    -- EN: group "API integration into your system"
    ('', 'en', 'api-integration', 'Payments and fintech API integration', 'payments-and-fintech-api-integration',
     'End-to-end integration of payment and fintech APIs with resilient status handling, webhooks, retries and reconciliation.',
     '<p>Payment reliability directly affects revenue and trust. We design integration flows with signature validation, duplicate-event protection, failure recovery and transparent diagnostics to reduce operational risk under real load.</p><p>Transaction lifecycle handling includes initiation, confirmation, cancellation, refund and exception states. Your team gets clear monitoring and incident visibility instead of manual troubleshooting loops.</p><p>The result is a production-grade payment backbone ready for scaling and cross-provider scenarios.</p>',
     100, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'api-integration', 'Analytics and marketing API integration', 'analytics-and-marketing-api-integration',
     'Unified growth data layer across ad platforms, analytics tools and CRM systems for decision-ready reporting.',
     '<p>Disconnected data creates confusion and slows growth decisions. We combine external APIs into a coherent model that links channel activity to qualified leads, sales outcomes and revenue impact.</p><p>Integration includes update scheduling, schema normalization, API limit handling and data quality validation. Reports stay stable, comparable and useful for cross-team planning.</p><p>Marketing, product and sales teams operate with one version of truth and can prioritize growth actions with confidence.</p>',
     110, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'api-integration', 'Industry API and internal service integration', 'industry-api-and-internal-service-integration',
     'Resilient integration architecture between external domain APIs and your internal product services.',
     '<p>When multiple providers are involved, integration quality defines operational stability. We design adapter layers, exchange contracts, idempotent workflows and queue-based processing to protect business logic from external API volatility.</p><p>Telemetry and SLA monitoring are embedded from the start: logs, metrics, alerts and bottleneck diagnostics for rapid incident response.</p><p>You get a dependable integration backbone that supports both current operations and future partner expansion.</p>',
     120, 1, NOW(), NOW()),

    -- EN: group "Consulting/expertise"
    ('', 'en', 'consulting-expertise', 'Product and architecture technical audit', 'product-and-architecture-technical-audit',
     'Deep audit of codebase, architecture and infrastructure with a prioritized, execution-focused improvement roadmap.',
     '<p>We assess scalability, reliability, security and delivery maturity against your business goals. Findings are translated into concrete risk-impact language so decision-makers understand what to fix first and why it matters.</p><p>The output is a practical roadmap: immediate fixes, phased improvements and ownership recommendations aligned with team capacity and release constraints.</p><p>This approach prevents random refactoring and helps teams deliver technical upgrades with measurable business value.</p>',
     130, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'consulting-expertise', 'B2B product consulting and growth strategy', 'b2b-product-consulting-and-growth-strategy',
     'Strategic consulting for B2B products: positioning, offer architecture, funnel design and KPI-driven growth execution.',
     '<p>We align product, marketing and engineering into one commercial model. Work starts with target-segment clarity and value framing, then moves to funnel structure, messaging hierarchy and retention logic.</p><p>We also define prioritized hypotheses with measurable KPIs so teams can run short cycles, evaluate impact and reallocate resources toward high-return initiatives.</p><p>The result is a focused growth trajectory where strategic decisions are grounded in market reality and execution capacity.</p>',
     140, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
    ('', 'en', 'consulting-expertise', 'Expert launch and release support', 'expert-launch-and-release-support',
     'Hands-on support for critical launches: readiness checks, risk control, execution alignment and post-release stabilization.',
     '<p>High-stakes launches fail when small gaps stack up across systems and teams. We validate launch readiness across infrastructure, integrations, analytics, conversion flow and incident-response protocols before release day.</p><p>During and after launch, we support triage, priority coordination and stabilization actions to reduce business impact and restore predictable operations quickly.</p><p>You gain a controlled release process with clearer risk visibility and faster recovery under pressure.</p>',
     150, 1, NOW(), NOW()),

    -- RU: group "AI"
    ('', 'ru', 'ai', 'Р Р°Р·СЂР°Р±РѕС‚РєР° AI Р°РіРµРЅС‚РѕРІ', 'razrabotka-ai-agentov',
     'РџСЂРѕРµРєС‚РёСЂСѓРµРј Рё РІРЅРµРґСЂСЏРµРј AI-Р°РіРµРЅС‚РѕРІ РїРѕРґ РІР°С€Рё Р±РёР·РЅРµСЃ-РїСЂРѕС†РµСЃСЃС‹: РїРѕРґРґРµСЂР¶РєР°, РїСЂРѕРґР°Р¶Рё, РІРЅСѓС‚СЂРµРЅРЅРёРµ РѕРїРµСЂР°С†РёРё Рё РѕР±СЂР°Р±РѕС‚РєР° РґР°РЅРЅС‹С….',
     '<p>РЇ СЃРѕР·РґР°СЋ AI-Р°РіРµРЅС‚РѕРІ, РєРѕС‚РѕСЂС‹Рµ СЂРµС€Р°СЋС‚ РєРѕРЅРєСЂРµС‚РЅС‹Рµ Р·Р°РґР°С‡Рё Р±РёР·РЅРµСЃР°: РѕС‚ Р°РІС‚РѕРјР°С‚РёР·Р°С†РёРё РїРѕРґРґРµСЂР¶РєРё Рё РєРІР°Р»РёС„РёРєР°С†РёРё Р»РёРґРѕРІ РґРѕ Р°СЃСЃРёСЃС‚РµРЅС‚РѕРІ РґР»СЏ РІРЅСѓС‚СЂРµРЅРЅРёС… РєРѕРјР°РЅРґ. РњС‹ РѕРїСЂРµРґРµР»СЏРµРј СЂРѕР»Рё, РїСЂР°РІР°, СЃС†РµРЅР°СЂРёРё РѕР±С‰РµРЅРёСЏ, РёСЃС‚РѕС‡РЅРёРєРё РґР°РЅРЅС‹С… Рё РіСЂР°РЅРёС†С‹ РѕС‚РІРµС‚СЃС‚РІРµРЅРЅРѕСЃС‚Рё Р°РіРµРЅС‚Р°, С‡С‚РѕР±С‹ РѕРЅ СѓСЃРёР»РёРІР°Р» РїСЂРѕС†РµСЃСЃС‹, Р° РЅРµ СЃРѕР·РґР°РІР°Р» С…Р°РѕСЃ.</p><p>РќР° СѓСЂРѕРІРЅРµ СЂРµР°Р»РёР·Р°С†РёРё РЅР°СЃС‚СЂР°РёРІР°СЋС‚СЃСЏ РёРЅС‚РµРіСЂР°С†РёРё СЃ CRM, Р±Р°Р·РѕР№ Р·РЅР°РЅРёР№, API Рё СЃРёСЃС‚РµРјР°РјРё СѓРІРµРґРѕРјР»РµРЅРёР№. РћС‚РґРµР»СЊРЅРѕ Р·Р°РєР»Р°РґС‹РІР°СЋС‚СЃСЏ РєРѕРЅС‚СЂРѕР»СЊ РєР°С‡РµСЃС‚РІР° РѕС‚РІРµС‚РѕРІ, Р¶СѓСЂРЅР°Р»РёСЂРѕРІР°РЅРёРµ РґРµР№СЃС‚РІРёР№, fallback-РјРµС…Р°РЅРёРєР° Рё РїРѕРЅСЏС‚РЅС‹Рµ РјРµС‚СЂРёРєРё СЌС„С„РµРєС‚РёРІРЅРѕСЃС‚Рё.</p><p>Р’ СЂРµР·СѓР»СЊС‚Р°С‚Рµ РІС‹ РїРѕР»СѓС‡Р°РµС‚Рµ СѓРїСЂР°РІР»СЏРµРјРѕРіРѕ AI-СЃРѕС‚СЂСѓРґРЅРёРєР°, РєРѕС‚РѕСЂС‹Р№ СѓСЃРєРѕСЂСЏРµС‚ РѕРїРµСЂР°С†РёРё, СЂР°Р·РіСЂСѓР¶Р°РµС‚ РєРѕРјР°РЅРґСѓ Рё РїРѕРІС‹С€Р°РµС‚ СЃРєРѕСЂРѕСЃС‚СЊ РїСЂРёРЅСЏС‚РёСЏ СЂРµС€РµРЅРёР№ Р±РµР· РїРѕС‚РµСЂРё РєРѕРЅС‚СЂРѕР»СЏ Рё РїСЂРѕР·СЂР°С‡РЅРѕСЃС‚Рё.</p>',
     160, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
